Package: uim
Version: 0.4.6
Revision: 5
Depends: gtk+2, gtk+2-shlibs, glib2-shlibs, pango1-xft2-shlibs
BuildDepends: x11-dev,gtk+2-dev, glib2-dev, pango1-xft2-dev, gettext-dev, intltool, pkgconfig, xml-parser-pm560 | xml-parser-pm580 | xml-parser-pm581
Recommends: skk-dict, prime, canna-server
Source: http://uim.freedesktop.org/releases/%n-%v.tar.gz
Source-MD5: a61636b7eb4cab6c09eb3d661d1d7db4
SetLDFLAGS: -L/usr/X11R6/lib -lX11
ConfigureParams: --libexecdir=%p/lib/%n
InstallScript: make install DESTDIR=%d
PostInstScript: <<
if [ configure = "$1" ]; then
    %p/sbin/update-gtk-immodules
fi
<<
PostRmScript: <<
if [ upgrade != "$1" ]; then
    %p/sbin/update-gtk-immodules
fi
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING ChangeLog INSTALL* NEWS README*
Description: Light-weight, full-featured input method lib
DescDetail: <<
UIM is a light weight and full featured input method library.

Most of the functionalites in this library are implemented
with Scheme. Thus it is simple, secure and flexible.
<<
